description:
Overall Objective&#58;  To contribute to community and institutional resilience in Gambella and Puntland by improving access to and quality of inclusive education in a safe and secure environment
-	SO1. To improve access to safe, quality pre-school and primary education in IDP and refugee camp settings and host communities;
-	SO2. To strengthen data collection for creating and disseminating a solid evidence base of what works to enhance access to quality and safe education in crisis-affected environments
